Recipe[s]: Extended Potion of Flame Legion Slaying

Rescuing Demmi from the pirates was only the first step. Although she's safe at the Order chapterhouse in Lion's Arch, Minister Caudecus's guard won't give up easily. Demmi has information critical to keeping Kryta's rightful Queen in power, and Caudecus can't afford for the Order of Whispers to find out what his daughter knows.
<c=@abilitytype>Device Kit.</c> Equip a kit that replaces your weapon with grenade skills.
<c=@abilitytype>Elixir.</c> Leap backward, spraying an acidic elixir on the ground that damages nearby foes.
Throw a ball of branded energy at your foe.

The Ministry Guard is unshakable, and Commander Landon is still following Demmi's trail. It's likely that Demmi Beetlestone never be free of her father's influence until she's stood up to his bullying thugs.
Slice your oppenent with your crystal fists.
Spit at your foe to confuse them.

Quaggan like this pointy stick. Makes quaggan scary like pirate."
—Duidda"
Confuse nearby foes with complex calculations.

A secret cavern on Stormbluff Isle hides the headquarters of one of the three great Orders of Tyria. From there, they fight against the rise of the Elder Dragons, seeking some way to put the monsters back to sleep.
